description:
This facility is optimized for language learners in language classes in the Arts College, but anyone is welcome. There is netprinting.

The larger room has 32 iMacs that will boot into either Windows 7 or Mac OS 10.6 (Snow Leopard). The smaller classroom, open any time it is not scheduled, has 16 similar iMacs. All stations have headsets for audio listening and recording. There are custom programs in Russian in Windows.

SCOLA is playing on a large-screen TV. For a password to download SCOLA broadcasts, write to rf10.

Corresponding textbooks are available for some language materials. CDs of Web Audio Lab, a program developed by the LRC and the Russian program, are available for sale and may be run for free on the computers.
keywords: Language Resource Center
